title: BRIEF-Netsol Signs Contract In Indonesia To Implement Ascent’S Suite Of Digital Apps

organizations.name: ascent’s suite of digital apps reuters

text:
April 12, 2018 / 1:14 PM / Updated 13 minutes ago BRIEF-Netsol Signs Contract In Indonesia To Implement Ascent’S Suite Of Digital Apps Reuters Staff 
April 12 (Reuters) - NetSol Technologies Inc: 
* CONTRACT INCLUDES PRODUCT LICENSE, 5-YR MAINTENANCE DEAL, AGREED UPON RATES FOR ADDITIONAL CUSTOMIZATION OF APPLICATION 
* DEAL WITH A FINANCE COMPANY IN INDONESIA TO DEPLOY ITS MOBILE ORIGINATION 
* YEAR MAINTENANCE DEAL, AGREED UPON RATES FOR ADDITIONAL CUSTOMIZATION OF APPLICATION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
